high_descs: Move across room to the small black table next to the trash bin.
Pick up the knife that is on the table.
Slice the apple that is on the same table.
Move across the room to the sink.
Slice the apple that is in the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Pick up a piece of apple from the sink.
Move across the room to the microwave.
Place the apple inside the microwave and allow it to cook.  Remove the apple from the microwave.
Move across the room to the small black table near the trash bin.
Place the apple slice on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Slice two apples with a knife. Cook part of one apple followed by placing on the table.

high_descs: Turn right, turn right again, walk towards the small black table
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle
Cut the apple on the table into slices
Turn right, walk straight, turn left towards the sink
Cut the apple inside the sink into slices
Put the knife inside the sink
Pick up a slice of the cut apple
Turn right, walk straight, turn left, walk towards the table with a white microwave
Open the microwave, put the apple inside, set the timer, open the microwave, take the apple, close the microwave
Turn left, turn left again, turn right towards the small black table
Put the apple on the small black table
anns.task_desc: Microwave a cut apple and put it on a black table.

high_descs: Go to the small black table on the right.
Take the knife on the table towards the back.
Cut the apple on the black table into three parts.
Take the knife to the sink on the right.
Cut the apple inside the sink into three parts.
Put the knife inside the sink.
Take one piece of the apple from the sink.
Turn around to take the apple to the microwave in the corner of the room.
Place the apple inside the microwave to heat it and then take it out.
Turn around and take the heated apple to the small black table.
Place the heated apple next to the the cut apple on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated cut apple next to a cut apple.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk to the black table, then turn right and walk to the small black shelf that is to the right of the counter
Pick up the knife from the first shelf of small black shelf
Slice the apple that is on the shelf closest to you
Turn to your right and walk to the sink that is to your left
Place the knife into the sink
Pick up a slice of apple from the sink
Turn around and head to the microwave that is to the left of the room
Open the microwave and place the apple slice on the plate inside, then turn on the microwave.
Open the microwave and pick up the apple slice then close the microwave
Turn around and head to the white table across the room, then turn left and walk to the black shelf in front of you.
Place the apple on the top of the shelf to the right of the sponge
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple on a shelf
